window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Grad student Jimmy has settled into life as a sorcerer with succubus Katarina, girlfriend Hayley, and familiar Charlotte. But much about his background and relationship to the infernal bureaucracy remains a mystery he struggles to unravel. Hired to recover a powerful grimoire lost by Hell decades ago, Jimmy and his harem come into contact with a mysterious group known as the Vermillion Cabal. But the threat the group poses is not what it seems, and the job soon leads to a shocking series of discoveries about Jimmy's past. With his life hanging in the balance, Jimmy must decide which path he will walk, and where his allegiances truly lieâ€”assuming those decisions have not already been made for him.</p> <p><b>Contains mature themes.</b></p>"; 
